<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="zh-cn">
<head>
	<meta charset="UTF-8">
	<title>我的Offer</title>
	<meta name="keywords" content="实力拍, 人才拍卖">
	<meta name="description" content="实力拍是深圳市红领巾网络科技有限公司旗下的项目">
	<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0, maximum-scale=1.0, user-scalable=0">
	<meta name="apple-mobile-web-app-capable" content="yes">
	<meta name="apple-mobile-web-app-status-bar-style" content="black">
	<meta name="format-detection" content="telephone=no">
	<meta name="format-detection" content="email=no">
	<link rel="shortcut icon" href="../img/logo_ico.ico">
	<link rel="stylesheet" type="text/css" href="../css/mobile/global.css">
	<link rel="stylesheet" type="text/css" href="../css/mobile/jobbidlist.css">
	
	<script src="../js/common/zepto.min.js"></script>
	<script src="../js/mobile/uiservice.js"></script>
	<script src="../js/mobile/jobbidlist.js"></script>
</head>
<body>
	<div class="viewport">
		<div class="list-wrap">
			<div class="show-con" id="main_content">
				<div class="query-bar box-shadow">
					<span class="query-item query-item-s" data-value=""><i>未处理</i></span>
					<span class="query-item" data-value="1"><i>已答应</i></span>
					<span class="query-item" data-value="2"><i class="b-r0">已拒绝</i></span>
				</div>
				
				<div class="con">
					<ul class="con-ul" id="list_content"></ul>
				</div>
			</div>
			
			<div id="reject_box">
				<div class="reject-con" >
					<div class="reject-title m-b10">拒绝理由</div>
					<ul class="reject-ul">
						<li class="reject-li reject-li-s" data-value="1"><i></i>薪资条件不合适</li>
						<li class="reject-li" data-value="2"><i></i>地点不合适</li>
						<li class="reject-li" data-value="3"><i></i>已经有更好的机会</li>
						<li class="reject-li" data-value="0"><i></i>其他</li>
					</ul>
					
					<div><textarea class="reject-area" id="reject_area" placeholder="请输入拒绝理由"></textarea></div>
				</div>
				
				<div class="reject-control">
					<span class="reject-cancle">返回</span>
					<span class="reject-submit">提交</span>
				</div>
			</div>
		</div>		
	</div>
</body>
</html>
